00:14:01,638 --> 00:14:02,680
have been studying a lot.

300
00:14:02,680 --> 00:14:03,890
And you've put payloads on this.

301
00:14:03,890 --> 00:14:05,140
So it shouldn't be new to you.

302
00:14:05,140 --> 00:14:10,930
But it's dramatic in its ability
to help us down that cost curve.

303
00:14:10,930 --> 00:14:13,310
The second part of
the cost curve--

304
00:14:13,310 --> 00:14:14,570
anybody know what this is?

305
00:14:14,570 --> 00:14:15,070
No.

306
00:14:15,070 --> 00:14:15,280
Rocket formula.

307
00:14:15,280 --> 00:14:16,132
Rocket formula.

