331
00:15:15,670 --> 00:15:19,900
But large rockets have
incredibly good mass fractions.

332
00:15:19,900 --> 00:15:23,850
And you can start seeing that in
the percentage of the propellant

333
00:15:23,850 --> 00:15:26,470
