484
00:22:27,110 --> 00:22:31,580
But we also have a secondary
hydrogen-oxygen engine.

485
00:22:31,580 --> 00:22:35,020
Different cycle, smaller,
10,000 pounds thrust engine,

486
00:22:35,020 --> 00:22:38,810
that we're developing, called
BE-7, that is available--

487
00:22:38,810 --> 00:22:42,400
think of it as the
